%%{init: {'theme': 'dark', 'sequence': {'actorMargin': 60, 'width': 160, 'useMaxWidth': false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Caller
    participant I as Inference plugin
    participant B as beforeCompletion
    participant WB as Workflow
    participant L as LLM
    participant A as afterCompletion
    participant WA as Workflow

    C->>I: chatComplete
    I->>B: invokeHook — full prompt
    B->>WB: ai.pii step
    WB-->>B: anonymized prompt + tokenMap
    B-->>I: anonymized prompt + tokenMap
    Note over I: Outside YAML expression boundary
    I->>L: connector call (stream)
    loop each chunk
        L-->>I: chunk
        I-->>C: de-anonymized chunk (sliding buffer)
    end
    I->>A: invokeHook — response + tokenMap
    Note over A: Expressions bind complete values
    A->>WA: transform.pii_restore step
    WA-->>A: restored response
    A-->>I: restored response
    I-->>C: final result
